Interface OraABNModelDetail

javax.datamining.base.ModelDetail
public interface OraABNModelDetail
extends javax.datamining.base.ModelDetail

OraABNModelDetail object is created for only singleFeature models. Rules can be retrieved for this type of model like a decision tree.
